title: Days of our Lives Thu, Aug 8, 2013
description:
As Cameron and Abigail grow closer, Chad meets with a specialist to find out if he really does have a brain tumor.


Nicole and Kristen clash.


Marlena goes ballistic when she learns Brady and Kristen are back together.


After a tense encounter with Justin, Adrienne fears her marriage may be over.


Rafe confides in Kate that he fears he might never walk again.


Kate privately works with Kayla.
